#. Tag: title
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1231
#, no-c-format
msgid "Chart"
msgstr "Diagram"

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use by placing a variable with name chartX (X=some text to make the variable "
"name unique) with a value project before the chart that shall be used."
msgstr ""
"Använd genom att placera en variabel kallad chartX (X=någon text för att "
"göra variabelnamnet unikt) med ett värde projekt innan diagrammet som ska "
"användas."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that the chart must be “anchored as character” or else the report "
"generator cannot find it."
msgstr ""
"Observera att diagrammet måste vara \"förankrat som tecken\" annars kan inte "
"rapportgeneratorn hitta det."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1236
#, no-c-format
msgid "The variable has this format:"
msgstr "Variabeln har detta format:"

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Variable: <varname>Name: chartX (X=some text) Value: project; "
"values=<replaceable>data</replaceable>;</varname>"
msgstr ""
"Variable: <varname>Name: chartX (X=någon text) Value: project; "
"values=<replaceable>data</replaceable>;</varname>"

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"where <replaceable>data</replaceable> is a comma separated list of values to "
"be include in the chart."
msgstr ""
"där <replaceable>data</replaceable> är en lista av värden åtskilda med "
"kommatecken som ska inkluderas i diagrammet."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1242
#, no-c-format
msgid "Possible <replaceable>data</replaceable> values are:"
msgstr "Möjliga värden på <replaceable>data</replaceable> är:"

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>bcws effort</guilabel> Budgeted cost of work scheduled, effort "
"based."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>bcws effort</guilabel> Insatsbaserad budgeterad kostnad av "
"schemalagt arbete."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>bcwp effort</guilabel> Budgeted cost of work performed, effort "
"based."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>bcwp effort</guilabel> Insatsbaserad budgeterad kostnad av utfört "
"arbete."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>acwp effort</guilabel> Actual cost of work performed, effort based."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>acwp effort</guilabel> Insatsbaserad verklig kostnad av utfört "
"arbete."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1248
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>spi effort</guilabel> Schedule performance index, effort based."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>spi effort</guilabel> Insatsbaserat schemalagd prestationsindex."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1249
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>cpi effort</guilabel> Cost performance index, effort based."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>cpi effort</guilabel> Insatsbaserat kostnadsprestationsindex."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>bcws cost</guilabel> Budgeted cost of work scheduled, cost based."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>bcws cost</guilabel> Kostnadsbaserad budgeterad kostnad av "
"schemalagt arbete."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>bcwp cost</guilabel> Budgeted cost of work performed, cost based."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>bcwp cost</guilabel> Kostnadsbaserad budgeterad kostnad av utfört "
"arbete."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>acwp cost</guilabel> Actual cost of work performed, cost based."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>acwp cost</guilabel> Kostnadsbaserad verklig kostnad av utfört "
"arbete."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1253
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>spi cost</guilabel> Schedule performance index, cost based."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>spi cost</guilabel> Kostnadsbaserat schemalagd prestationsindex."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1254
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>cpi cost</guilabel> Cost performance index, cost based."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>cpi cost</guilabel> Kostnadsbaserat kostnadsprestationsindex."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The charts you create in your template must have the same (or more) number "
"of columns as the number of values you specify in your variable."
msgstr ""
"Diagrammen du skapar in mallen måste ha lika många (eller fler) kolumner som "
"antal värden du anger i variabeln."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "Exempel:"

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Variable name: <varname>chart1</varname> Value: <varname>project; "
"values=bcws cost,bcwp cost, acwp cost;</varname>"
msgstr ""
"Variable name: <varname>chart1</varname> Value: <varname>project; "
"values=bcws cost,bcwp cost, acwp cost;</varname>"

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:1262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that you cannot mix effort- and cost-based values. If you want to show "
"both, create two charts."
msgstr ""
"Observera att du inte kan blanda insats- och kostnadsbaserade värden. Om du "
"vill visa båda, skapa två diagram."

